	(text "Protection Calculation\n\nP-Channel MOSFET - DMP6023LFG7\n- Vds: -60V\n- Rds(ON): 25mOhm @ Vgs = -10V\n- Id(max): -7.7A @ Vgs = -10V\n- Vgs(max): +/- 20V\n\nPicking Vgs = 15V (Zener MM5Z15VT1G)\n\nTVS Diode (SMF33A)\n- Vrwm = 33V\n- Vclamping = 53.3V\n\nClamp:\n53.3 < 60V (mosfet) - so will clamp safely so mosfet should survive\n\nPass-Through\n33V > 26.1 (6S liHV) - so will pass that voltage, even not fully charged 8s\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 447.04 49.53 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "a1f8deb2-45e9-49fc-858a-3f114bd01b7b")
	)
